<section id="Creating_a_Virtual_Machine_or_Template_Report" remap="TID_15121">
	<title>Creating a Virtual Machine or Template Report</title>
	<para>
		For a listing of virtual machines and templates, you can create a quick report in CSV, TXT, or PDF formats.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To Create a Resource Report</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Infrastructure</guimenu><guisubmenu>Virtual Machines</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click the accordion for the items for report creation.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2107.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject><guibutton>(Download)</guibutton>.
			</para>
			<itemizedlist>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						Click 
						<inlinemediaobject>
							<imageobject>
								<imagedata fileref="images/2132.png" />
							</imageobject>
						</inlinemediaobject> for a TXT file.
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						Click 
						<inlinemediaobject>
							<imageobject>
								<imagedata fileref="images/2133.png" />
							</imageobject>
						</inlinemediaobject> for a CSV file.
					</para>
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					<para>
						Click 
						<inlinemediaobject>
							<imageobject>
								<imagedata fileref="images/2134.png" />
							</imageobject>
						</inlinemediaobject> for a PDF file.
					</para>
				</listitem>
			</itemizedlist>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>